      "content": "honestly i dont even know why i bother trying anymore. it’s just the same thing every single time. i get a job, i mess it up. i try to stay sober, i relapse. i meet someone, i ruin it. it’s like i’m just wired to fail and then i have to deal with the fallout all over again. i’m just so tired of the cycle. it never actually changes.",
